- No, it's got to be...
- Okay.

59
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:54,040
- Okay, Nick.
- It's a coincidence.

60
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:04,520
How many times have you
watched that, by the way?

61
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,000
I'm just listening to music.

62
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,640
Of course you are.

63
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,120
Silly me.

64
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:15,120
<i>Existence is a circle, recurring.</i>

65
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:19,640
<i>And in every recurrence,
you and I sit in this room.</i>

66
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:23,520
<i>You ask me your questions,
I tell you the truth.</i>

67
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:27,160
