76
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,640
- Lucy, I think it might be...
- No.

77
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,080
He's never gonna see Mike again.

78
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,760
- With supervised visits...
- He left him.

79
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:02,840
He closed the door,
and he left him there to burn.

80
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,880
If I could prove it,
he would be in prison, but I can't.

81
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:10,320
- And you still don't believe me.
- It's a recurring nightmare.

82
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:13,320
- Based on a memory.
- A traumatic memory.

83
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:16,880
Muddled. Blended with imagination.

84
