104
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,280
Come on.

105
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,080
Got some bits for your room.

106
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,200
Five.

107
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,960
- Fifteen.
- Hmm!

108
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,960
It's all right.

109
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,960
It's just the house settling.

110
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:28,880
