122
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,800
Just for this lifetime, yeah?

123
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:15,400
This loop.

124
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,120
I'm not supposed to be here.

125
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,760
There's no such thing as "supposed to."

126
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:26,280
We're here because we choose to be.

127
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:32,120
Just like I chose to have you.

128
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:45,480
And I'm choosing to win this game!

129
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,360
Oi, mate!

130
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,400
Where you going?

131
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,640
- Walk away.
- What?

132
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,400
What's that, paedo?

133
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,360
- Why are you dressed like a paedo?
- Oi, catch!

134
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,680
Eh!

135
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:16,360
Give us your money or we'll report you
for being a fucking paedo.

136
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,960
I don't want to hurt you,

137
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,160
so just walk awa... Uhh!

138
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:23,120
Grab his phone! Quick, grab his phone!

139
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,400
Aargh!

140
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,520
Aargh!

141
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,720
Aaargh!

142
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,440
Aargh!

143
