<i>♪ I saw love in your eyes ♪</i>

145
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:09,600
<i>♪ Made me feel so warm inside ♪</i>

146
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:12,360
<i>♪ Now look at me, baby ♪</i>

147
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,440
<i>♪ And what do you see? ♪</i>

148
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:17,640
<i>- ♪ You see love in my eyes ♪</i>
- Dhillon, are you listening to me?

149
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,600
Dhillon!

150
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:21,920
Sorry.

151
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,400
Don't faint on me.

152
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,680
Mnh-mnh.

153
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,160
Jesus Christ!

154
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:28,920
Just tell me what I need to know.

155
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,120
Victim was struck three times.

156
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:33,720
Skull fractures here, here and here.

157
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,520
This blow ruptured a blood vessel.

158
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:39,640
Cause of death, it was an intercranial
hematoma. Not instant.

159
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,640
That's why he was still walking around?

160
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,320
- He bled out.
- No, bled in.

161
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:45,880
Bleed was between the brain and the skull.

162
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,960
Oh, for fuck's sake.

163
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:50,680
- Is there anything else?
- Nothing relevant.

164
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,960
Death from head trauma, open and shut.
You can charge your man.

165
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:56,400
- Right.
- Don't let him escape.

166
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,840
Hilarious. Get some
new material, Gibson.

167
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:09,080
DI Dhillon.

168
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,720
<i>Ravi, it's Sam.</i>

169
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,480
Sam Boyd.

170
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,680
Boyd?

171
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:16,640
Hi. Sorry, new phone.

172
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,440
<i>- Haven't got your number saved.</i>
- Yeah.

173
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,320
Sorry to call out of the blue but...

174
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,800
<i>Not a problem. You after a reference?</i>

175
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:25,840
A favour, a big one.

176
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:29,600
And you're gonna say no,
but I'm gonna keep on asking.

177
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,360
Of course you are.

178
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:38,200
